comments:
If a model contains an attribute with a default value and a custom type that cannot be instantiated by the default factory, EFactoryImpl, validating the model result in an IllegalArgumentException being thrown by createFromString(). Since validation is automatically invoked on starting the generator, this unhandled exception prevents the generator from even opening.

It is not uncommon to model an EDataType and then implement a capable factory implementation after generating code.
